  "text": "The second wave of Wnt-signaling is driven by the activation of wnt8 in the germring, by Nodal-signaling emanating from the yolk syncitial layer (YSL) [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . As this signal is circumferential, dorsal transcriptional repressors counteract its effects by inhibiting the activation of wnt8 in this region.",
